description: A woman and her two daughters died in Poland after winds tore the roof off a ski rental shop.
title: Storm Ciara kills at least seven in Europe
title_page: Storm Ciara kills at least seven in Europe - BBC News
maintext: Transport shut down and schools were forced to close across Belgium, Germany, Luxembourg and the Netherlands. Dutch authorities reported traffic jams of more than 720km (448 miles) across the country on Monday, and there was still some flight disruption on Tuesday after airlines cancelled hundreds of journeys.
